Recommends: softkms-pkcs11
Description: Modern Software Key Management System
 softKMS is a secure, modern alternative to SoftHSM with HD wallet
 support, written in Rust. It provides enterprise key management,
 hierarchical deterministic (HD) wallets, and PKCS#11 compatibility.
 .
 Features:
  - Secure key storage with AES-256-GCM encryption
  - Multi-tenant identity isolation
  - BIP32/BIP44 hierarchical deterministic keys
  - Ed25519, P-256, and post-quantum Falcon signatures
  - gRPC, REST, and CLI interfaces
  - Complete audit logging

Package: softkms-pkcs11
Architecture: any
Depends: softkms (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: PKCS#11 module for softKMS
 This package provides the PKCS#11 cryptographic token interface
 for softKMS, allowing integration with existing applications
 that use the PKCS#11 standard.
